---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CTABanner from '../../components/CTABanner.astro';
---

<Layout title="Denver Preschool Program Case Study | Upfront" description="See how Denver Preschool Program launched a new application and Preschool Finder Tool powered by Upfront to help Denver families access quality preschool.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <a href="/case-studies" class="inline-flex items-center text-brand-teal hover:text-brand-teal/80 transition-colors mb-8">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
        </svg>
        Back to Case Studies
      </a>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 mb-8">
        <img
          src="/images/partners/denver-preschool-program.png"
          alt="Denver Preschool Program logo"
          class="h-16 w-auto"
        />
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">
        Denver Preschool Program
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-gray">
        New Application and Online Search for Denver Families
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Overview -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray mb-6">
        For nearly two decades, Denver Preschool Program (DPP) has helped to ensure that every Denver child has access to high-quality preschool, regardless of income or neighborhood.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray">
        DPP launched a new application and Preschool Finder Tool — powered by Upfront — designed to make life easier for families seeking preschool and for providers serving them. This platform combines real-time data, streamlined applications, and accessible design into one seamless experience, while still providing the individualized support that families and providers know and trust.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Smarter Online Search -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-brand-light">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <span class="inline-block text-sm font-semibold text-brand-teal uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
        For Families
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">
        Smarter Online Search for Families
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray mb-6">
        Families can now use the new Preschool Finder Tool at <strong>find.dpp.org</strong> to explore preschool options across Denver. The new tool includes:
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-teal mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">Real-time vacancy data so families can immediately see which programs have open spots</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-teal mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">Last updated timestamps so parents know how current the information is</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-teal mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">A seamless provider experience to keep vacancy data accurate and up to date</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-teal mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">Accessibility by design with WCAG 2.1 compliance and translation into more than 10 languages</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray">
        This means families can not only find the right preschool but also confirm availability without making endless phone calls or relying on outdated lists.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Streamlined Application -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <span class="inline-block text-sm font-semibold text-brand-orange uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
        Application Process
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">
        A Streamlined Application Process
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray mb-6">
        The application has been redesigned to save families time and reduce frustration. Key improvements include:
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">Eligibility Screening Upfront</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Families who are not currently eligible are flagged early, avoiding wasted time while still capturing their contact information for future outreach.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">Integrated Provider Data</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Families can view which programs have open spots while applying, allowing them to select programs immediately without needing to call each one.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">Mobile-Friendly Upload</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Families can securely upload required documents straight from their phones, enabling on-the-go applications.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Analytics and Impact -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-brand-light">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <span class="inline-block text-sm font-semibold text-brand-teal uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
        Behind the Scenes
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">
        Analytics and Impact
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray">
        In addition to creating a better user experience, the platform equips DPP with powerful analytics to understand how families navigate the process, where drop-offs occur, and how to further improve access. This real-time insight allows DPP to reach more families effectively and ensure providers are connected to the children who need them.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- New Era -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">
          A New Era for Preschool Access in Denver
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray mb-6">
          Denver Preschool Program has long been a leader in expanding access to early childhood education. With this launch, families have a smarter, simpler way to find preschool, providers have a stronger way to connect with families, and the city has a data-driven system to support equity and access.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray">
          Upfront is proud to partner with DPP and MetrixIQ on this transformation — ensuring that every family in Denver can more easily find and afford the preschool their child deserves.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABanner />
</Layout>
